\title{Split monomorphism}
\meta{external}{https://ncatlab.org/nlab/show/split+monomorphism}

\subtree{
  \taxon{definition}

  \p{A \em{split monomorphism} is a morphism with a right inverse (which is a \em{split epimorphism}).}
}

\p{Split monomorphisms are preserved by all [functors](math-000E).}

\p{A morphism is a isomorphism iff it is an epimorphism and a split monomorphism.}

